      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782558970456,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Sharding\n\nAccess patterns\n\nQ. get obejct by id\nQ. get all objects in a bucket\nQ. get all versions for object id\n\n\nshard by : bucketid and objectid",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Sharding\n\nAccess patterns\n\nQ. get obejct by id\nQ. get all objects in a bucket\nQ. get all versions for object id\n\n\nshard by : bucketid and objectid",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "4GfUGIZgale9xY_G03GTf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1698,
      "y": 1360,
      "width": 421.47161865234375,
      "height": 280,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b7C",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 749108718,
      "version": 312,
      "versionNonce": 579293230,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782558970456,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Optimise for small and large files storage\n\nSmall file can be appended to one large file ( like WAL)\nlarge files can be split in chunks of 4 mb and uploaded\n\n\nChecksum for correctnes of data\n\nVersioning : TIMEUUID\nin metadata storage\n\n\nGC :\nremove file which are duplicate, orphan, deleted",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Optimise for small and large files storage\n\nSmall file can be appended to one large file ( like WAL)\nlarge files can be split in chunks of 4 mb and uploaded\n\n\nChecksum for correctnes of data\n\nVersioning : TIMEUUID\nin metadata storage\n\n\nGC :\nremove file which are duplicate, orphan, deleted",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
